Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish the mailpony\Nwould just come already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait another minute to find out\Nif Rainbow Dash got in or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, you're more nervous\Nthan Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not nervous at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get into\Nthe Wonderbolt Academy--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get in!\NIf you get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't jinx it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you,\Nit's in the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't jinx it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the best flyer in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm probably the best flyer\Nin all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if they just went ahead,\Nand made me a Wonderbolt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.49,0:00:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a letter here\Nfor Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I... didn't get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are so gullible.\NLike I wasn't gonna get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just sooooooooo\Nhappy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... thanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie?\NI kinda need to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner I get there,\Nsooner I get to show off my stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.95,0:01:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,See you guys in a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,DON'T FORGET TO WRITE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think she heard me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 3 | Episode 7\NWonderbolt Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed by GrayJeager\NFr.Jeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/GhxBronie\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!\NThis is gonna be sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well lookie what we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet y'all think you're\NWonderbolt material, don't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you got what it takes\Nto be an elite flyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.\NLet me be the first to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU DON'T!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had what it took\Nto be an elite flyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd already be\Na Wonderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Still think\Nyou're something special?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya think you're hot stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you're the worst flyer\Nin the whole academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll probably quit\Nafter the first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No ma'am!\NI'd never quit, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet you couldn't fly past the\Nfirst flypole without getting winded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you\Nwhat I've got, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a chance\Nto prove yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then,\Nnow's your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me five hundred laps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lap four-hundred and ninety-nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One more lap to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Five hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad!\NFor a couple of newbies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Name's Lightning Dust.\N- Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna grab some grub\Nin the mess hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, Rainbow Dash hasn't\Nbeen gone twenty-four hours yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her a chance\Nto settle in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just go see\Nwhat Twilight's up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear Princess Celestia's got her\Nworking on some new spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,New spells, huh?\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not here when\NRainbow Dash's letter arrives,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able\Nto read it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I don't read it right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to write\Nher back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I don't write\Nher back right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,she might think\NI didn't get her letter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she might worry\Nit got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and if she's worried about her letter\Nshe'll be distracted,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and if she's distracted then\Nshe won't do well at the academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and if she doesn't do well at the academy,\Nthen she'll get kicked out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and if she gets kicked out, she'll never\Nbe allowed to be a Wonderbolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and if she doesn't get\Nto be a Wonderbolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,all her dreams\Nwill be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will be\Nall... my... FAULT!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words,\Nyou're stickin' by the mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts are the fastest,\Nbest precision flyers in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But spinouts can still happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a Wonderbolt must\Nbe able to recover quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This... is the Dizzitron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna make you very,\NI repeat, very dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your task is to try and recover,\Nand fly straight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you have recovered,\Nyou must come in for a smooth landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who's first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're up.\N- Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ready?\N- Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen seconds.\NDecent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't go\Nwritin' home about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Rainbow Dash.\NLet's see what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Six seconds?!\NThat's an academy record.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it look so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I make everything look easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Lightning Dust,\Nyou're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, can you put\Nthe Dizzitron at maximum speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna push my limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. You asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Six point five seconds.\NNot bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony even came close\Nto six seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They should make us\NWonderbolts right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they should!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For the rest of the camp,\Nyou'll be working in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning,\NI'll post the teams
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,including who'll be lead pony,\Nand who'll be wing pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Like we're gonna need it!\N- Heh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which one of you lucky gals\Ngets to be my wing pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You might wanna check the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A wing pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They made us a team!\NIsn't that awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Permission to enter, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the best time on the Dizzitron!\NOnly six seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you made me a wing pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believe you and Lightning Dust\Nwill be an unstoppable team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not think\Nyou'll be an unstoppable team?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!\NI mean, no ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... We'll be\Nan unstoppable team, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I should be lead pony,\Nma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think Lightning Dust likes to push\Nherself a little harder than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I made her lead pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Got it?\N- Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Today you will all be participating\Nin the flag hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll divide you into two teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Red, and blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever finds the most flags\Nof the opposing team's color wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is gonna be\Nso much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think this is going to be fun,\Nyou are sadly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for training purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not recess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead ponies and wing ponies\Nmust fly together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If any pair splits apart,\Nthey will be immediately disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ready to rock and roll?\N- Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- You spotted any flags yet?\N- Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There's one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We should slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like both of us\Ncan make it at this speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning Dust and Rainbow Dash\Nfound the first flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!\NLet's find some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.\NJust give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish we could help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that could possibly help me\Nis a letter from Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been three days already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, she probably doesn't\Neven know our names anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably can't\Nremember our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Pinkie Pie?\NI never heard of a Pinkie Pie!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is Pinkie Pie?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're so worried, then\Nwhy don't you send her a letter first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course!\NThat's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wait!\NI got an even better idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we send Rainbow Dash\Na care package?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,\Nbefore she forgets all about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, come on,\Nlet's face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But, maybe it'll jog\Nher memory somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, I'm sure Rainbow Dash still\Nremembers our faces and who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think sending her\Na care package is a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A care package it is!\NWe'll send it through the mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,WAIT! Ah!\NThat won't work at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what if the package\Ngets lost in the mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What if somepony else\Ngets the package by accident
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she remembers us\Ninstead of Rainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she becomes\Nour new friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the real Rainbow Dash\Nwouldn't ever know that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,she used to have friends\Nand she forgot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anypony else following this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll deliver the care package\Nto Rainbow Dash in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wouldn't mind a little trip.\N- I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Count me in!\N- Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Me five!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't be upset if\Nshe doesn't recognize you at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It may take a while for her\Nto get her memory back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll be doing\Nour famous air obstacle course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The object of this exercise\Nis to work on your precision flying
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,under extreme circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't worry about winning.\NIt's not a race.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everypony,\Nget on your marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, can't they go any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good,\NI can't get around them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can still fly completely in sync\Nand blow Spitfire's mind with our moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they,\Na couple of snails?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a little weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance\Nto pass these slowpokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad!\NAnd in record time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely made the right decision\Nmaking you two a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The others seem\Nto have had a little trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with the precision part\Nof the exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better go help\Nsort them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you two\Ngo hit the mess hall early?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Lightning Dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, maybe we don't\Ncut the other teams off like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you snooze, you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Wonderbolts are supposed\Nto be able to recover from a spinout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw them on the Dizzitron!\NThey could use the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not our fault we're\Nso much better than those other guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not every pony is destined\Nto become a Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the best of the best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course I'm right!\NNow let's go fuel up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kicking all that tail\Nhas made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea about how we can\Nliterally blow away our competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're already way ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lightning Dust likes to push herself\Na little harder than you do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I made her lead pony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow my lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a twister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooooo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You... remember me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yeah,\Nof course I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But what are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to bring you\Na care package.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't realize you'd be in the middle\Nof some crazy tornado drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That... was... awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends could have been\Nsmashed to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but they weren't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't say the same for the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We totally wiped them out\Nwith that tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The other cadets will have\Nto be up there for days
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to bust as many as we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A hoof bump?\NSeriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me clip my wing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you sent half of our class into serious\Ntail spins on the obstacle course,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you unleashed a tornado\Nthat nearly demolished my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? And?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I get that\Nyou wanna be the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're going about it\Nin the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts\Ndon't seem to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Spitfire did make me\Nthe leader and you the wing pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This better be important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be up there\Nbusting clouds with your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done with that, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Already?\NThat's an academy record!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain your methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning Dust decided to use\Na tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit excessive for cloud-busting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But judging from your time,\Nit was obviously an effective tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well that "effective tactic"\Nnearly took out my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No disrespect ma'am,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's a big difference between\Npushing yourself as hard as you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and just being reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And if being reckless is what\Ngets rewarded around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if that's what it means\Nto be a Wonderbolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,then I don't want any part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, newbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a Wonderbolt\Nwas your dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Rainbow Dash.\NI know how much this meant to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you storm out of my office\Nwithout giving me a chance to respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts are looking for\Nthe best flyers in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,being the best should never come\Nat the expense of our fellow ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just about\Npushing ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about pushing ourselves\Nin the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown that\Nyou're capable of doing just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no wing pony,\NRainbow Dash...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohmygoshohmygoshohmygosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get out there\Nand give me twenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even get to open\Nyour care package!
